Libertini, 1930, Il Museo Biscari",[242,243,244,245],"Q2SBPG9F","2EUC82DH","DQDPC573","SKUU2R8X",[247,248,249,24,29,33,250,251,252,253,251,254,255,124],"isic001298","funerary inscription of euporios",{"_":5},"catina","catania","sicilia","sicily","museo civico di catania","ancient greek",[],{"title":258,"body":259,"divs":260,"editions":287,"images":306,"handnote":312},"ISic001298. Funerary inscription of Euporios","\u003Cdiv id=\"editions\">\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive\" lang=\"grc\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-interpretive\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Εὐπορίου\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐπορίου\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Εὐπορίου\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Εὐπόριος\">Εὐπορίου\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-interpretive-simple-lemmatized\">  \u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Cspan data-text=\"Εὐπορίου\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Εὐπόριος\">Εὐπορίου\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/div>  \u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Ca id=\"al1-diplomatic\">\u003C!--0-->\u003C/a>\u003Cspan class=\"linenumber\">1\u003C/span>\u003Cspan data-type=\"persname\" data-name-type=\"attested\" data-text=\"Εὐπορίου\">\u003Cspan data-type=\"name\" data-name-type=\"\" data-text=\"Εὐπορίου\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Εὐπορίου\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Εὐπόριος\">ΕΥΠΟΡΙΟΥ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv class=\"attribution\">Text encoding: Victoria Fendel, Robert Crellin\u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id=\"edition-diplomatic-simple-lemmatized\">\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-diplomatic\">\u003Cspan data-text=\"Εὐπορίου\" data-n=\"5\" data-lemma=\"Εὐπόριος\">ΕΥΠΟΡΙΟΥ\u003C/span>\u003C/span>\u003C/div>\u003Cp class=\"miniapp\">\u003C/p>\u003C/div>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"facsimile-images\">\u003Ch2>Facsimile Images\u003C/h2>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001298_tiled.tif\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001298_tiled-thumb.tif\">\u003C/a>\u003Ca href=\"ISic001298.jpg\">\u003Cimg title=\"I.Sicily with the permission of the Assessorato Regionale dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana - Dipartimento dei Beni Culturali e dell’Identità Siciliana\" src=\"ISic001298-thumb.jpg\">\u003C/a>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"apparatus\">\u003Ch4>Apparatus criticus\u003C/h4>\u003Cul>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan>  \u003Cspan>Text based on photograph\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>; \u003C/li>\u003Cli>\u003Cspan class=\"line 1\">line.1: \u003Cspan>Libertini: ΕΥΦΟΡΙΩΝ\u003C/span>  \u003C/span>\u003C/li>\u003C/ul>\u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>English translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Of Euporios.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"translation\">\u003Ch2>Italian translation\u003C/h2>\u003Cp class=\"translation-author\">\u003Ca href=\"https://orcid.org/0000-0001-5187-5163\">Marta Fogagnolo\u003C/a>\u003C/p>  \u003Cp>Di Euporios.\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"commentary\">\u003Ch2>commentary\u003C/h2>  \u003Cp>Kaibel and Libertini linked the block to a relief in volcanic rock depicting two armed gladiators, which represented an advertisement for a gladiatorial show, but, as Manganaro notes, any connection between the relief and this funerary inscription must be ruled out. The name \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Εὐπόριος\u003C/span> is not attested elsewhere, while in the female form, \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Εὐπορία\u003C/span>/\u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">Euporia\u003C/span>, is attested in a Latin inscription of the imperial period from Catania (CIL 10.7052 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000336\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000336\u003C/a>) and in a Christian inscription from Syracuse (Strazzulla 1897: 183 no. 344 = MARPO inv.15558).\u003C/p>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"bibliography\">\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Kaibel 1890 \u003Ca href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">475\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Hoffmann 1904 5240 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Libertini 1930 43 no. 85 tav. 26 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001871\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001871\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 83 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1988 56 n.281 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003C/div>  \u003Cdiv id=\"handnote\"> \u003Cp>Lunate Ε.\u003C/p> Line 1  60-80   \u003C/div>\u003Cdiv id