/span> is not attested elsewhere, while in the female form, \u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"grc\">Εὐπορία\u003C/span>/\u003Cspan class=\"lang\" lang=\"la\">Euporia\u003C/span>, is attested in a Latin inscription of the imperial period from Catania (CIL 10.7052 = \u003Ca href=\"http://sicily.classics.ox.ac.uk/inscription/ISic000336\" target=\"_blank\">ISic000336\u003C/a>) and in a Christian inscription from Syracuse (Strazzulla 1897: 183 no. 344 = MARPO inv.15558).\u003C/p>  ",{"id":279,"html":280},"bibliography","\u003Ch2>bibliography\u003C/h2>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Kaibel 1890 \u003Ca href=\"https://clio.columbia.edu/catalog/6873760\" target=\"_blank\">475\u003C/a>  \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001072\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Hoffmann 1904 5240 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000817\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Libertini 1930 43 no. 85 tav. 26 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001871\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001871\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003Cli> Korhonen 2004 83 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10000028\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  \u003Cul>\u003Cli> Manganaro 1988 56 n.281 \u003Ca href=\"https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\" target=\"_blank\">https://biblio.inscriptiones.org/epig10001427\u003C/a>  \u003C/li>\u003C/ul>  ",{"id":282,"html":283},"handnote"," \u003Cp>Lunate Ε.\u003C/p> Line 1  60-80   ",{"id":285,"html":286},"license"," Licensed under a Creative Commons-Attribution 4.0 licence. ",[288,290,293,295,298,299,302,303],{"html":289},"Text encoding: Marta Fogagnolo",{"id":291,"lang":124,"html":292},"edition-interpretive","\u003Cdiv class=\"textpart\" lang=\"grc\">\u003Cspan class=\"ab\" id=\"div-interpretive\">  \u003Ca id=\"al1-i